Package: ibdsegments
Title: Identity by Descent Probability in Pedigrees
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maarten", "Kruijver", , "maarten.kruijver@esr.cri.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6890-7632"))
Description: Tools for Identity by Descent (IBD) in pedigrees. A Hidden Markov 
    Model is used to compute identity coefficients, simulate IBD segments and 
    to derive the distribution of total IBD sharing and segment count across 
    chromosomes.
